(785, 'Newsletter Pusdatin Edisi April 2025', 'publikasi', 'Edisi April 2025, Volume 22 No. 04', '1411-9196', '2025-04-30', '6,0', 12, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Newsletter Pusdatin adalah publikasi yang berisi\r\ninformasi dan liputan kegiatan di lingkup Pusdatin. Newsletter terbit setiap\r\nbulan dan disebarluaskan dalam bentuk <i>softcopy<o:p></o:p></i></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Newsletter edisi April 2025 berisi :<br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Source Sans Pro, sans-serif">• Pusdatin dan BB Mektan Gelar&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">Diskusi Mekanisasi Pertanian&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">Mendukung Smart Farming,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">Halaman 1</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Source Sans Pro, sans-serif">• Penguatan Peran Remote Sensing&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">Untuk Pertanian Berkelanjutan Earth&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">Observation: Diving Impact For a</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Source Sans Pro, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp;Resilient Indonesia, Halaman 5</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Source Sans Pro, sans-serif">• Panen R